<Input><Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">Find the solutions of the following <Font bold="true">difference equations</Font> and plot them graphically.

(a) x(n+2) - 5x(n+1) + 6x(n) = 0;    x0 = 1; x1 = 1;</Text-field>
</Input>
</Group></Presentation-Block><Presentation-Block>
<Group view="presentation" inline-output="false" labelreference="L445" drawlabel="true" applyint="true" applyrational="true" applyexponent="false">
