<Input><Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"><Font bold="true">TEST - EXERCISE 1
HINT KEY WORDS: difference equation, sequence</Font>

Find the solution for the following difference equations:

<Font bold="true">Difference equation:</Font>
a) x_{n+1} = [(n+1)/(n+2)]^2 * x_{n} + [1/(n+2)]     , where x_{0}=1

<Font bold="true">Higher-order difference equation:</Font>
b) x_{n+3} - 4 * x_{n+2} = x_{n+1} + 6 * x_{n} = 60 * 4^[n]   , where x_{0}=2, x_{1}=12, x_{2}=12

<Font bold="true">Non-linear difference equation:</Font>
c) x_{n+1} = ( 2 * x_{n} ) / ( 1 + 4 * x_{n} )    ,where x_{0}=1, Hint: use substitution x_{n} = 1/y_{n}<Equation executable="true" style="2D Math" input-equation="" display="LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYnLUkjbWlHRiQ2I1EhRicvJSVib2xkR1EmZmFsc2VGJy8lK2ZvcmVncm91bmRHUShbMCwwLDBdRicvJStleGVjdXRhYmxlR0YxLyUsbWF0aHZhcmlhbnRHUSdub3JtYWxGJw==">LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYjLUkjbWlHRiQ2I1EhRic=</Equation></Text-field>
</Input>
