<Input><Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">
b)   / x'(t) = -3 * x(t) + 4 * y(t)
<Font encoding="UTF-8">      \134 y'(t) = -2 * x(t) + 3 * y(t)
</Font>
c)   / x'(t) = -x(t) - y(t)
<Font encoding="UTF-8">      \134 y'(t) = x(t) - 3 * y(t)
</Font>
d)   / x'(t) = -2 * x(t)
<Font encoding="UTF-8">      \134 y'(t) = -4 * x(t) - 2 * y(t)
</Font>
