<Input><Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal">a)   / x'(t) = y(t)
<Font encoding="UTF-8">      \134 y'(t) = x(t) * (1 - x^2(t)) + y(t)
</Font>
b)   / x'(t) = -2 * x(t) + y(t) + 2
<Font encoding="UTF-8">      \134 y'(t) = x(t) * y(t)
</Font>
c)   / x'(t) = y^2(t)
<Font encoding="UTF-8">      \134 y'(t) = x(t)
</Font>
d)   / x'(t) = x^2(t) - y^2(t)
<Font encoding="UTF-8">      \134 y'(t) = x(t) * y(t) - 1</Font></Text-field>
</Input>
